---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Tuhin Mohanta | Enterprise Platform Engineering Leader | ISB CTO Programme"
  description="Enterprise Technology & Platform Engineering Leader specializing in large-scale modernization, AI-ready systems, DevOps transformation, and regulated healthcare platforms. ISB CTO Programme & Leadership with AI. 20+ years building scalable enterprise architectures.">


<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-eyebrow"><strong>Enterprise Technology & Platform Engineering Leader</strong><div style="line-height:1.6">Modernizing Systems · Scaling Teams · Enabling AI-Ready Enterprises</div><div style="height:.8rem"></div><div>ISB Chief Technology Officer Programme | ISB Leadership with AI</div></div>
        <h1>Engineering leader who builds<span class="line-accent">organizations that scale.</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-desc">Two decades of architecting enterprise platforms and building high-performance engineering organizations across cloud, platform, and product engineering. I operate at the intersection of strategy, technology, and people – with deep ownership of outcomes.</p>
        <div class="hero-meta-row">
          <div class="hero-meta-item"><span class="label">Current</span><span class="value">Senior Manager, Software Engineering (Head of Platform Engineering) – Oracle Health</span></div>
          <div class="hero-meta-item"><span class="label">Credentials</span><span class="value">ISB CTO · ISB Leadership with AI</span></div>
          <div class="hero-meta-item"><span class="label">Based in</span><span class="value">Bengaluru, India</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-portrait">
        <div class="portrait-frame">
          <picture>
            <source
              type="image/avif"
              srcset="/profile-sm.avif 400w, /profile-md.avif 800w"
              sizes="(max-width: 640px) 400px, 800px"
            />
            <source
              type="image/webp"
              srcset="/profile-sm.webp 400w, /profile-md.webp 800w"
              sizes="(max-width: 640px) 400px, 800px"
            />
            <img
              src="/profile-md.jpg"
              srcset="/profile-sm.jpg 400w, /profile-md.jpg 800w"
              sizes="(max-width: 640px) 400px, 800px"
              alt="Tuhin Mohanta - VP / Head of Engineering"
              loading="eager"
              width="800"
              height="684"
            />
          </picture>
          <div class="portrait-glow"></div>
          <div class="portrait-line portrait-line-1"></div>
          <div class="portrait-line portrait-line-2"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-separator"></div>
</section>

<div class="impact-strip">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="impact-row">
      <div class="impact-item"><div class="impact-number">$2B<span class="unit">+</span></div><div class="impact-desc">Portfolio Scale</div></div>
      <div class="impact-divider"></div>
      <div class="impact-item"><div class="impact-number">550<span class="unit">+</span></div><div class="impact-desc">Engineers Led</div></div>
      <div class="impact-divider"></div>
      <div class="impact-item"><div class="impact-number">$25M<span class="unit">+</span></div><div class="impact-desc">Cost Savings Delivered</div></div>
      <div class="impact-divider"></div>
      <div class="impact-item"><div class="impact-number">99.9<span class="unit">%</span></div><div class="impact-desc">Platform Uptime</div></div>
      <div class="impact-divider"></div>
      <div class="impact-item"><div class="impact-number">50<span class="unit">+</span></div><div class="impact-desc">Global Deployments</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- EXECUTIVE PRESENCE -->
<section class="presence" id="presence">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="presence-headline fade-in">
      <div class="section-label" style="justify-content:center">Executive Presence</div>
      <h2>A leader who thinks in <em>systems</em>,<br>operates with <em>conviction</em>,<br>and leads with <em>humanity.</em></h2>
      <p>I don't just manage engineering – I build the organizational muscle that lets technology compound. Every system I've designed, every team I've built, reflects a belief: that scale without soul is fragile, and speed without strategy is noise.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="presence-pillars fade-in">
      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><svg class="icon icon-lg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Strategic Depth</h3>
        <p>Sees three moves ahead. Connects platform architecture to business outcomes, aligning engineering investment with organizational trajectory.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><svg class="icon icon-lg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Analytical Precision</h3>
        <p>Data-driven in decision-making. Operates with rigor - measuring what matters, questioning assumptions, and course-correcting with discipline.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><svg class="icon icon-lg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Humane Leadership</h3>
        <p>Builds trust before building systems. Creates environments where engineers do their best work – through psychological safety, mentorship, and genuine care.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon"><svg class="icon icon-lg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Deep Ownership</h3>
        <p>No delegation of accountability. Takes end-to-end responsibility from vision to production - and holds the line when it matters most.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="signature-strip fade-in">
      <div class="sig-item">
        <div class="sig-icon"><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg></div>
        <div><h4>Scale with Speed</h4><p>Built and scaled platforms serving 50+ deployments globally. Designed CI/CD frameworks that cut deployment cycles by 60%. Operates at enterprise velocity without sacrificing quality.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sig-item">
        <div class="sig-icon"><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></div>
        <div><h4>Accuracy Under Pressure</h4><p>99.9% uptime across mission-critical platforms. Zero post-release defects on foundational systems. Builds quality into culture, not just process.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sig-item">
        <div class="sig-icon"><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"/><path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.46 0"/></svg></div>
        <div><h4>Accountability as Practice</h4><p>Owns the outcome, not just the activity. Champions blameless culture while maintaining sharp personal accountability. The buck stops here - always.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label fade-in">About</div>
    <h2 class="section-title fade-in">The person behind<br>the <em>engineering.</em></h2>
    <div class="about-grid fade-in">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>I'm an enterprise platform engineering leader and ISB-Certified Chief Technology Officer with 20+ years building scalable systems and high-performance organizations. My career spans embedded systems, telecom, mobile platforms, enterprise architecture, and healthcare technology leadership – always at the intersection of deep technical complexity and organizational impact.</p>
        <p>Currently at Oracle Health, I lead platform modernization and cloud migration strategy for a $2B+ product portfolio across 50+ global deployments with 550+ engineers. I specialize in building AI-ready enterprise systems, DevOps transformation, and regulated enterprise platforms. My identity isn't tied to one industry – wherever I go, I build engineering organizations that are fast, precise, accountable, and deeply human.</p>
        <p>I hold dual executive certifications from ISB – Chief Technology Officer Programme and Leadership with AI – equipping me with both enterprise architecture thinking and AI governance frameworks that modern technology organizations demand.</p>
        <p>Outside work, I write about engineering leadership, AI governance, technology strategy, and the culture of excellence. I believe the best engineering leaders are those who make themselves invisible – building teams so strong that the system runs without them.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="credential-row">
        <div class="credential">
          <div class="cred-icon"><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c6 3 12 0 12 0v-5"/></svg></div>
          <div><h4>ISB-Certified Chief Technology Officer</h4><p>Indian School of Business Executive Education · 2024–2025</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="credential">
          <div class="cred-icon"><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v4a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="12" y2="22"/></svg></div>
          <div><h4>ISB Leadership with AI Programme</h4><p>Strategic AI governance, responsible AI, and AI-era leadership</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="credential">
          <div class="cred-icon"><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg></div>
          <div><h4>20+ Years in Enterprise Engineering</h4><p>Oracle · Cerner · Siemens · Samsung · Nokia · MindTree</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="credential">
          <div class="cred-icon"><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 20V10"/><path d="M18 20V4"/><path d="M6 20v-4"/></svg></div>
          <div><h4>Certified Scrum Master · ITIL</h4><p>Process excellence, agile at scale, value stream optimization</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="philosophy">
  <div class="container">
    <blockquote>"Build a team so strong, no one knows who the leader is. That's not invisibility – that's the highest form of leadership."</blockquote>
    <div class="attribution">– Tuhin Mohanta</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- EXPERIENCE -->
<section id="experience" style="background:var(--bg-deep)">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label fade-in">Journey</div>
    <h2 class="section-title fade-in">Building at scale,<br><em>across domains.</em></h2>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item current">
        <div class="timeline-period">Sep 2022 – Present</div>
        <div class="timeline-role">Sr. Manager, Software Development</div>
        <div class="timeline-company">Oracle Health · Bengaluru</div>
        <div class="timeline-desc">Leading platform modernization and cloud migration strategy for Oracle's healthcare product portfolio – a $2B+ digital transformation across 50+ global deployments. Architected enterprise DevOps CI/CD platform reducing deployment cycles by 60%. Managing $25M+ in cloud infrastructure optimization. Driving AI transformation strategy with GenAI-augmented DevOps and AI governance frameworks for regulated enterprise systems.</div>
        <div class="timeline-tags"><span>Platform Modernization</span><span>Cloud Migration</span><span>Enterprise DevOps</span><span>AI Governance</span><span>Healthcare Tech</span><span>$2B+ Portfolio</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-period">Aug 2015 – Sep 2022</div>
        <div class="timeline-role">Engineering Manager | Sr. Engineering Manager</div>
        <div class="timeline-company">Cerner Corporation · Bengaluru</div>
        <div class="timeline-desc">Scaled DevOps transformation from 12 to 200+ engineers. Built enterprise-wide Site Reliability Engineering (SRE) function. Achieved 99.9% uptime for mission-critical healthcare platforms. Led cloud infrastructure optimization and enterprise DevOps practices. Won 2x KNOTT Awards (Cerner's highest engineering honor). Top-rated keynote speaker at global tech conferences for 5 consecutive years.</div>
        <div class="timeline-tags"><span>DevOps Transformation</span><span>Site Reliability Engineering</span><span>Enterprise DevOps</span><span>Cloud Infrastructure</span><span>Healthcare Tech</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-period">Oct 2012 – Aug 2015</div>
        <div class="timeline-role">DevOps Practice Lead</div>
        <div class="timeline-company">Siemens Healthcare · Bengaluru</div>
        <div class="timeline-desc">Established enterprise DevOps practice from ground zero. Built CI/CD pipelines that reduced release cycles from weeks to hours. Led regulated enterprise systems compliance integration (FDA/IEC) for healthcare technology platforms. Won Siemens Innovator's Award for tooling automation.</div>
        <div class="timeline-tags"><span>DevOps Transformation</span><span>Regulated Enterprise Systems</span><span>Healthcare Technology</span><span>FDA Compliance</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-period">Oct 2007 – Sep 2012</div>
        <div class="timeline-role">Lead Integration Engineer</div>
        <div class="timeline-company">Samsung · Nokia · Novell · Bengaluru</div>
        <div class="timeline-desc">Directed system integration for Samsung's Linux mobile platform, cutting delivery timelines by 40%. Represented Samsung at global Linux Mobile Consortium. Lead Integration Engineer for Nokia's Symbian Platform. Certificate of Appreciation from Samsung Research, South Korea.</div>
        <div class="timeline-tags"><span>Linux</span><span>Mobile Platforms</span><span>System Integration</span><span>LiMo</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-period">Sep 2005 – Oct 2007</div>
        <div class="timeline-role">Senior Engineer</div>
        <div class="timeline-company">MindTree Consulting · Bengaluru</div>
        <div class="timeline-desc">R&D Services – protocol verification for Alcatel-Lucent. Developed 9,000+ lines of verification code. Built bootloaders and device drivers. Delivered mission-critical projects with zero post-release defects.</div>
        <div class="timeline-tags"><span>Embedded Systems</span><span>TCL</span><span>Device Drivers</span><span>Telecom</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

